name: Astro Canine
description: A lost dog called Patch ends up in a dog’s home where no one claimed her so due to her smartness she get’s put on a top secret project which would take her to space. The project run by A.I.C. and A.S.N.A. didn’t go to well and half way through her mission in space they lose all contact with her. Now she faces space alone in a new spaceship she found and if it’s just her luck a alien cat species who hate humans and dogs have heard of her arrival and plan to cat nap her, fight through the waves of enemies and help Patch come home.
